column2: SELECT TOP #   p.cModelMag_g,  p.cModelMag_r,   p.cModelMag_i,   p.cModelMag_z,   p.cModelMagErr_g,   p.cModelMagErr_r,   p.cModelMagErr_i,   p.cModelMagErr_z,   p.objID,  p.ra,   p.dec,   s.z,   s.zErr,   s.ra,   s.dec FROM Galaxy as p LEFT JOIN SpecPhoto as s ON p.objID = s.objID
